<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-81-1169 </DOCNO><TEXT>A calculational method permitting to control the content of impuritiesin a scintillation detector working substance is suggested. The equation,describing the relation between {gamma}-radiation field functional disturbancesand the detector working substance change, is obtained.</TEXT></DOC>